{"word":"κατόπτης","slug":"κατόπτης","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κατόπτης</b></el> <el>(κατ-όπτης, ου,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ὄψομαι</el>, <a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> of <a href='S:ὁράω'><el>ὁράω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a spy, scout</i>, <b>Hhymn.</b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>an overseer</i>, <el>τῶν πραγμάτων</el> <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}